{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-124-ordered-radicals","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 124: organizovani koreni","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Radikal od $n$, $rad(n)$, je proizvod različitih primordnih delitelja $n$. Na primer, $504 = 2^3 × 3^2 × 7$, stoga $rad(504) = 2 × 3 × 7 = 42$.</p>\n<p>Ako izračunamo $rad(n)$ za $1 ≤ n ≤ 10$, zatim sortiranjem po $rad(n)$, i sortiranjem po $n$ ako su vrednosti korena jednake, dobijamo:</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\">$Bado haijapangwa$</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td colspan=\"3\">$Imepangwa$</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>$n$</td>\n        <td>$rad(n)$</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>$n$</td>\n        <td>$rad(n)$</td>\n        <td>$k$</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>1</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>4</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>4</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>8</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>4</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>5</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>6</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>9</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>7</td>\n        <td>7</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>5</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n        <td>7</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>8</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>6</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n        <td>8</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>9</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>7</td>\n        <td>7</td>\n        <td>9</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>10</td>\n        <td>10</td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>10</td>\n        <td>10</td>\n        <td>10</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div><br>\n<p>Neka je $E(k)$ element $k$-ti u sortiranoj sekvenci $n$; na primer, $E(4) = 8$ i $E(6) = 9$. Ako je $rad(n)$ sortirano za $1 ≤ n ≤ 100000$, pronađi $E(10000)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3e81000cf542c50fefb","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301751,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-124-ordered-radicals"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function orderedRadicals() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\norderedRadicals();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>orderedRadicals()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>21417</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(orderedRadicals(), 21417);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-124-ordered-radicals","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChal